    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been well-maintained throughout its life. Mechanically, it is very sound; the engine runs smoothly, the transmission shifts as it should, and all major systems are fully functional. The interior is clean with only minor signs of wear on the driver's seat and floor mats. On the exterior, the paint still holds a nice gloss, though you will find a few small stone chips on the hood and a light scratch on the rear bumper. This is a dependable, high-quality car that is ready for many more miles of reliable service.",
