    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presented for your consideration is an automotive specimen of the highest caliber. This vehicle remains in concours-level condition, having been preserved with uncompromising attention to detail. Every surface, from the flawless exterior finish to the pristine interior appointments, reflects a standard of care synonymous with showroom delivery. Mechanically superlative and aesthetically beyond reproach, this offering represents a rare opportunity for the discerning collector who demands nothing less than perfection.",
