    {
      "id": "sybil_12_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_12",
      "description": "Hey there! You've seriously got to see this beauty in person\u2014it's honestly like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I've taken absolute pride in keeping it in pristine, mint condition. It looks stunning, runs like an absolute dream, and is totally ready for its next big adventure with you. If you're looking for a ride that\u2019s been loved and cared for perfectly, this is definitely the one. Treat yourself to a car that feels brand new!",
