    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "This vehicle is a true collector-grade specimen, meticulously maintained in a climate-controlled garage since day one. The exterior boasts a deep, mirror-like finish with zero paint chips or swirl marks, protected by a professional-grade ceramic coating that makes the color pop. Inside, the cabin remains pristine and smoke-free; the premium leather seats are supple with no bolster wear, and the original floor mats look untouched. Every button, sensor, and electronic feature functions exactly as it did the day it left the showroom. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, supported by a comprehensive folder of service records from certified technicians. Recent preventative maintenance includes a full synthetic fluid flush and a fresh set of high-performance tires. This is an investment-quality car for a buyer who demands the absolute best and refuses to compromise on condition.",
      "price": 46900.0,
