      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 43
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Presented in impeccable, showroom-ready condition, this vehicle represents the pinnacle of automotive preservation. Every surface, from the flawless exterior finish to the pristine interior, reflects a history of meticulous care and professional maintenance. This is an investment-grade example intended for the discerning buyer who demands nothing less than absolute perfection in their next acquisition.",
