      "description": "Hey there! You have got to see this beauty\u2014it honestly looks like it just rolled off the showroom floor. I have taken such good care of it, and it is in absolutely pristine shape. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s basically flawless and ready for a new home, this is the one! Feel free to reach out if you want to take a look!",
