      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offered is an investment-grade E46 M3, featuring the legendary S54 naturally aspirated inline-six with individual throttle bodies and high-pressure double VANOS. This specimen boasts a meticulously maintained drivetrain, including documented rod bearing replacement and a reinforced rear subframe to ensure structural integrity under high lateral loads. Power is delivered through a Getrag six-speed manual transmission to a M-Variable Lock differential, providing surgical precision and mechanical grip. The factory finish remains flawless, free of stone chips or clear coat degradation, while the interior retains the original matte texture of the Nappa leather. This is a turn-key example for the discerning collector seeking peak analog performance.",
